title: The Amazing Spider-Man 2 Rendered 720p (greek subs) by kozanitis
description:
H deuteri tainia tis neas ekdosis tou Spiderman poy paixtike prosfata stous kinimatografous. Molis simera vrika tous protous ellinikous ypotitlous pou eutixos tairiazoun me to hdcam video pou eixa anevasei prin apo merikes meres.

I poiotita tou video vlepetai an axaireseia kapoia, elaxista eutyxos. spasimata stin eikona. Auto einai to timima pou plironei kapoios otan thelei na dei to video prin akomi vgei stin agora to DVD.

I eikona exei analysi 720p: 1024x528. O ixos einai molis ypofertos, eutyxos pou yparxoun oi allinikoi ypotitloi gia na mporeite na katalavete tous dialogous.

Kali diaskedasi.
